sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Shopware Storefront
    participant L as Product listing (100k)

    Note over B,L: BEFORE — synchronous (~3200 ms)
    B->>S: GET /
    S->>L: load listing of all 100k products
    L-->>S: result (~1600 ms) + render (~1500 ms)
    S-->>B: full HTML (~3200 ms)

    Note over B,L: AFTER — deferred (~200 ms shell)
    B->>S: GET /
    S-->>B: HTML shell with placeholder (~200 ms)
    B->>S: async GET /widgets/cms/navigation/{id}
    S->>L: load listing
    L-->>S: result
    S-->>B: listing HTML (~1600 ms, in background)
    Note over B: page visible immediately,<br/>products appear after
